introduction 1 in these proceedings, asic claims that the defendant, citigroup global markets australia pty limited, breached fiduciary duties to its client, toll holdings limited, and engaged in insider trading by dealing in shares in patrick corporation on 19 august 2005.
2 prior to that date toll had retained citigroup to provide corporate advisory services to toll including advice in relation to a proposed takeover by toll of patrick.
